PN,41601
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1772658364
OL,3,CCouple on bucket-list Dubai trip
OL,4,Cdesperate for UK return sleeping in
OL,5,Clobby
OL,7,FA retired couple from Sussex, sleeping
OL,8,Fin the reception of their holiday
OL,9,Frental apartment block, and an Oxford
OL,10,Funiversity student on her own, are
OL,11,Famong those trying to get home from
OL,12,FDubai amid escalating fighting in the
OL,13,FMiddle East.
OL,15,FNick Westwood, a retired train driver
OL,16,Ffrom Barnham, West Sussex, and his
OL,17,Fwife Joanne, a retired credit analyst,
OL,18,Fare in Dubai for their 'bucket-list'
OL,19,Fholiday but have been forced to extend
OL,20,Ftheir seven-day stay.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1772658364
OL,3,CCouple on bucket-list Dubai trip
OL,4,Cdesperate for UK return sleeping in
OL,5,Clobby
OL,7,FWith no indication as to when they'll
OL,8,Fbe able to get a flight back home,
OL,9,Fit's becoming a costly trip with the
OL,10,Fpair paying an extra #81.00 per night
OL,11,Fto remain at their accommodation,
OL,12,Fwhich is only available until Thursday.
OL,14,FAs the room is on the 25th floor the
OL,15,FWestwood's have been sleeping in the
OL,16,Flobby of the high-rise building so
OL,17,Fthey're able to make a quick exit
OL,18,Fshould there be any missile strikes.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1772658364
OL,3,CCouple on bucket-list Dubai trip
OL,4,Cdesperate for UK return sleeping in
OL,5,Clobby
OL,7,FNick told ITV News, "We should have
OL,8,Fleft on Sunday. The last couple of
OL,9,Fdays, been very terrifying and
OL,10,Ffrightening here, it's a very
OL,11,Fstressful situation.
OL,13,F"The last couple of nights we've slept
OL,14,Fdown in the reception area to stay
OL,15,Fsafe, and obviously for a quick exit
OL,16,Fif we needed to, but haven't felt
OL,17,Fcomfortable being up here.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1772658364
OL,3,CCouple on bucket-list Dubai trip
OL,4,Cdesperate for UK return sleeping in
OL,5,Clobby
OL,7,FJoanne said, "We never thought in a
OL,8,Fmillion years would end up in the
OL,9,Fmiddle of a warzone. And I don't say
OL,10,Fthat lightly or exaggerating.
OL,12,F'When things started on Saturday, we
OL,13,Fwere literally on our balcony, looking
OL,14,Fout, and we could see missiles and
OL,15,Fdrones just being shot at the sky and
OL,16,Fwe could hear it all.
OL,18,F"You do rather feel that we've been
OL,19,Fleft to our own devices to try and
OL,20,Fsort ourselves out."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1772658364
OL,3,CCouple on bucket-list Dubai trip
OL,4,Cdesperate for UK return sleeping in
OL,5,Clobby
OL,7,FAround 300,000 British Citizens are
OL,8,Fbelieved to be in Gulf countries
OL,9,Ftargeted by Iran, and 102,000 have
OL,10,Fregistered their presence within the
OL,11,Fregion.
OL,13,FRapid deployment teams are being sent
OL,14,Fto the region to assist British
OL,15,Fnationals on the ground and the
OL,16,Fmajority of departures from the region
OL,17,Fremain cancelled.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1772658364
OL,3,CCouple on bucket-list Dubai trip
OL,4,Cdesperate for UK return sleeping in
OL,5,Clobby
OL,7,FOxford-Brookes University journalism
OL,8,Fstudent Cassandra San Carlos is stuck,
OL,9,Fand without her family, who managed to
OL,10,Fget a flight back to their home in
OL,11,FFrance before tensions escalated.
OL,13,FShe'd been with them in Dubai for a
OL,14,Fholiday and was due to board a flight
OL,15,Fto Heathrow when the explosions
OL,16,Fhappened.
OL,18,FCassandra San Carlos tells ITV News
OL,19,Fshe is constantly anxious as she
OL,20,Fawaits news about how she will get
OL,21,Fback to the UK
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1772658364
OL,3,CCouple on bucket-list Dubai trip
OL,4,Cdesperate for UK return sleeping in
OL,5,Clobby
OL,7,FDescribing the moment as 'terrifying',
OL,8,Fshe said she's felt anxious ever since
OL,9,Fextremely concerned about what might
OL,10,Fhappen next.
OL,12,F"Yesterday morning I was woken up by
OL,13,Fexplosions. Last night I was also
OL,14,Fwoken up by explosions. You're never
OL,15,Ffeeling well because you're always
OL,16,Fanxious about the situation, what will
OL,17,Fwhat will happen next? When will be
OL,18,Fthe next explosion?
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1772658364
OL,3,CCouple on bucket-list Dubai trip
OL,4,Cdesperate for UK return sleeping in
OL,5,Clobby
OL,7,F"When I was here, on Saturday night, I
OL,8,Freceived an alarm in my phone telling
OL,9,Fme to hide from from windows because
OL,10,Fof explosion and it was so terrifying."
OL,12,FDesperate to get on a flight out of
OL,13,Fthe Middle East, Cassandra says she is
OL,14,Fhaving to rely on information from
OL,15,Fsocial media to find out what's going
OL,16,Fon.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1772658364
OL,3,CCouple on bucket-list Dubai trip
OL,4,Cdesperate for UK return sleeping in
OL,5,Clobby
OL,7,F"I just want to go to Europe. I just
OL,8,Fwant to take a flight and just leave
OL,9,Fthis place because I'm terrified. We
OL,10,Fdon't any information I don't care
OL,11,Fabout the company. If I can just leave
OL,12,Fhere, I'm happy. "
OL,14,FAirlines are trying to get more
OL,15,FBritish passengers back home, but they
OL,16,Fare operating what they call select
OL,17,Fflights as and when it is safe to do
OL,18,Fso. Airlines have told passengers not
OL,19,Fto go the airports in the Middle East,
OL,20,Fbut to wait to be contacted.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1772658364
OL,3,CCouple on bucket-list Dubai trip
OL,4,Cdesperate for UK return sleeping in
OL,5,Clobby
OL,7,FEmirates plans to operate two flights
OL,8,Fto Heathrow and one each to Gatwick
OL,9,Fand Manchester.
OL,11,FAt least some of these flights will be
OL,12,Foperated by the airline's A380 jets,
OL,13,Fwhich can each carry up to 615
OL,14,Fpassengers depending on how they are
OL,15,Fconfigured.
OL,17,FCustomers with earlier bookings are
OL,18,Fbeing treated as a priority, and
OL,19,Fanyone who has been rebooked will be
OL,20,Fcontacted directly by the airline.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1772658364
OL,3,CCouple on bucket-list Dubai trip
OL,4,Cdesperate for UK return sleeping in
OL,5,Clobby
OL,7,FQatar Airways - which usually serves
OL,8,FHeathrow and Gatwick from Qatar - said
OL,9,Fon Tuesday morning that its operations
OL,10,Fremain suspended because of the
OL,11,Fclosure of Qatari airspace.
OL,13,FBritish Airways cancelled its
OL,14,Ftimetabled flights to Heathrow from
OL,15,FAbu Dhabi, Amman, Bahrain, Doha and
OL,16,FDubai on Tuesday.
OL,18,FThe airline told passengers: "We are
OL,19,Fclosely monitoring the situation and
OL,20,Fhave cancelled a number of our flights
OL,21,Fto the Middle East.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G11/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41612
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1772658364
OL,3,CCouple on bucket-list Dubai trip
OL,4,Cdesperate for UK return sleeping in
OL,5,Clobby
OL,7,F"Safety is always our top priority and
OL,8,Fwe would never operate a flight unless
OL,9,Fit was safe to do so."
OL,11,FPassengers with bookings on certain
OL,12,Froutes up to March 15 are being
OL,13,Fallowed to amend the date to fly on or
OL,14,Fbefore March 29.
OL,16,FVirgin Atlantic axed a flight from
OL,17,FDubai to Heathrow. The conflict
OL,18,Fbetween Iran and the US and its allies
OL,19,Fhas caused widespread airspace
OL,20,Fclosures in the Middle East, sparking
OL,21,Fmajor disruption to flights.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G12/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
