FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41613
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1772658364
OL,3,CCouple on bucket-list Dubai trip
OL,4,Cdesperate for UK return sleeping in
OL,5,Clobby
OL,7,FAbout half a million passengers per
OL,8,Fday use airports in Dubai, Doha or Abu
OL,9,FDhabi, which are vital hubs for travel
OL,10,Fbetween Europe and the continents of
OL,11,FAsia and Australia. It is likely to
OL,12,Ftake several days to clear the backlog
OL,13,Fof passengers.
OL,15,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,16,Four political experts are across all
OL,17,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,18,Fto the latest episode below...
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G13/13
